    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登竞选团队坚称“没问题”，但退出压力越来越大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-fine-campaign-insists-as-pressure-to-drop-out-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名顾问周四表示，总统乔·拜登在新冠病毒检测呈阳性后的第二天情况“良好”。但他的竞选活动却不太好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-fine-campaign-insists-as-pressure-to-drop-out-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:38:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚提高最低工资以缓解生活成本危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/nigeria-bumps-up-minimum-wage-to-help-ease-cost-of-living-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚计划将最低工资提高一倍以上，结束与工会长达数月的讨价还价，在工人罢工期间，尼日利亚电网和最繁忙的机场被迫关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/nigeria-bumps-up-minimum-wage-to-help-ease-cost-of-living-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:24:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国对运送俄罗斯石油的油轮船队实施更多制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/uk-piles-more-sanctions-on-fleet-of-tankers-moving-russian-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国对另外 11 艘帮助俄罗斯向客户出口石油的油轮实施了制裁，其中包括一些属于影子船队的油轮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/uk-piles-more-sanctions-on-fleet-of-tankers-moving-russian-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:19:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼与欧盟发生口角，其欧洲议会议员反对冯德莱恩的新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/meloni-eu-spat-on-show-as-her-meps-oppose-new-von-der-leyen-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔治亚·梅洛尼领导的布鲁塞尔议会议员投票反对乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩连任欧盟委员会主席，凸显了意大利总理与欧盟机构之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/meloni-eu-spat-on-show-as-her-meps-oppose-new-von-der-leyen-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:08:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国被指囤积天然气供应捷克共和国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/germany-accused-of-hoarding-gas-meant-to-supply-czech-republic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国指责德国在该地区努力寻找俄罗斯天然气替代供应之际，通过削减出口管道的容量来囤积天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/germany-accused-of-hoarding-gas-meant-to-supply-czech-republic</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 14:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威领导人称美国总统不想放弃乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/norway-s-leader-says-no-us-president-wants-to-abandon-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威首相表示，他不认为美国总统会撤回对乌克兰的支持或放弃北约，因为防御联盟惠及所有成员国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/norway-s-leader-says-no-us-president-wants-to-abandon-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 14:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国金币销量因对工党财政计划的担忧而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/uk-gold-coin-sales-jump-on-concerns-over-labour-s-fiscal-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者担心新工党政府可能改变财政政策，英国皇家铸币厂的免税金币销量在上个季度出现增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/uk-gold-coin-sales-jump-on-concerns-over-labour-s-fiscal-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 13:15:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列议会在最新与美国的冲突中回避两国解决方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/israel-s-parliament-backs-resolution-opposing-palestinian-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列议会通过决议，正式反对建立独立的巴勒斯坦国，并警告称巴勒斯坦国可能成为恐怖组织的基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/israel-s-parliament-backs-resolution-opposing-palestinian-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其特使访问尼日尔以确保铀供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/turkey-top-envoy-goes-to-niger-in-bid-to-secure-uranium-supplies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其外交部长、国防部长和能源部长周三访问了尼日尔，以确保能够开采这个西非国家的丰富铀矿。]]></description>
